Package: uimm
Type: Package
Title: An universe of individual level mortality models
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    c(person(given = "Xiaochuan", family = "Lu", email = "xiaochuan.lu@unsw.edu.au",
             role = c("aut", "cre")))
Description: S4 classes and methods for parametric age-cohort (PAC) survival models 
    (Gompertz, Makeham, Perks, Beard, Kannisto, Thatcher), with fitting, evaluation 
    (AIC, IBS), a formula interface, survival trees with left-truncation, 
    model-based recursive partitioning, and a Gompertz proportional hazards wrapper.
